rComments: Prof. Jacqmin is an absolutely amazing prof! He always goes through the material thoroughly and always takes questions during the lecture! He's also super accessible and always willing to answer questions! I was terrible at Math in high school and he made Math my favourite course at University!

Prof Jacqmin is a wonderful prof. I hate math and tend to do horrible in it, but he really made it understandable. Go to class and take notes! He does sample problems and explains them on the board really well. Do the past MT's and finals. You dont get part- marks on the assessments so be really careful. Attend DGD's if you have a good instructor.

Although he is not the best at providing explanations in class and his handwriting is pretty illegible, both his midterm exams as well as his final exam were incredibly straightforward and similar to the exams from previous years. He is also easy to talk to outside of class, and is always willing to answer questions.
